	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinae</placeName> 30. Maii 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas proxime datas per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonum</placeName> nobilem accepi, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName> amice et domine charissime; per quas te mirari intelligo, quod neque a domino <persName ref="p1548" cert="high">Richardo</persName>, nec <persName ref="p1560" cert="high">Hopero</persName>, nec ullo alio ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> quid acceperis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">pro amico nostro <persName ref="p1548" cert="high">Richardo</persName> respondere ausus sim, quod tui immemor non est, sed per op[p]ortunitatem scripturus, ut promiserat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Impediunt tamen tum negotia valde magna, tum linguae Latinae et scribendi inexperientia, quam solet accusare; aut potius timor, ne quid scribendo peccet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad haec non solet rumorum et famae, sed veritatis esse scriptor; atque ob id perquam raro ad me nova scribit: sed quae scribit solent esse vera.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non igitur dubito, quin quum verum aliquid noverit et certum de statu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliae</placeName> nostrae, tum mihi tum tibi id sit scripturus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Religionis liber aeditus est, idque consensu procerum et totius consilii, quod nos parleamentum vocamus, verum nondum impressus: non dubito, quin mittat quum primum prodierit.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> et <persName ref="p4744" cert="high">Paulus Fagius</persName> tuto pervenerunt in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName>, atque ab aula <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1255" cert="high">Cantuariensis</placeName> huc scripserunt.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam eundem non pervertant aut pejorem redant!</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8041" cert="high">Ioannes a Lasco</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName> reliquit, sed reversurus eo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1560" cert="high">Ioannes Hoperus</persName> cum suis salve pervenerunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Andwerpiam</placeName>, atque tandem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> sunt.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Andwerpia</placeName> mihi scripsit, (vult?) ut te salutarem et totam ecclesiam illius et uxoris nomine.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De Caesa[re ni]hil, quam quod <placeName ref="l1284" cert="high">Bruxellae</placeName> adhuc sit, licet fama fuit eum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l168" cert="high">Gan[davum]</placeName> fuisse profectum.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dictum praeterea est, eum venturum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l471" cert="high">Speiram</placeName>, atque [cer]tum est <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l471" cert="high">Speirenses</placeName> praeparasse hospitia sibi et suis; sed potior venit [rumor,] nempe eum non venturum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliae</placeName>, ut solet, cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglis</placeName> foedus et pacem violat.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Septies namque uno die magno impetu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2122">Boloniam</placeName> adorsus est, sed suo malo; nam toties passus est repulsam cum militum jactura non parva.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scoti</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallorum</placeName> promissis freti insolescunt, sed in illorum magnum malum: nam iterum a nostris caesi sunt ducenti, quingenti capti.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesar</persName>, ut audio, concessit regi nostro in defensionem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2122">Boloniae</placeName> decem millia peditum, equitum quingentos.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam liceret de pace potius quam de bello scribere!</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetos</placeName> in defensionem aut potius recuperationem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2122">Boloniae</placeName> vocat <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galus</placeName>, non imprudenter facit; sed <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetii</placeName> imprudentissime, si consenserint, nam nimium a vobis distat.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam tamen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetii</placeName> se inter hos duos principes interponerent, ut de pace agerent atque id conditionibus aliquibus iustis, per quas ea recuperari et firmari posset!</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam timendum est, ne, dum mus et rana certet, aquila utrumque devoret.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> nostra haec sunt scribenda, nempe quod praeter omnem humanam expectationem adhuc ut antehac manemus; nihil immutatum, quam quod festi interim dies et ieiunium praecipitur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orate dominum pro nobis assidue quum in privatis tum in publicis precibus vestris atque gratias nobiscum agite pro hoc divino suo beneficio.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutato uxorem et doctos quosque meo nomine.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p505" cert="high">Burcherus</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglus</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrico Bullingero</persName>, amico longe charo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
